{"tid":383741,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實點解明知人地當自己朋友都表白","createTime":"2017-09-01T16:54:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T03:13:58.000Z","uid":141235,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f595332806c2fd5711728fa4e7f5cab9eb9bdace","tid":383741,"uid":141235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T16:54:27.000Z","msg":"以為表完白放低到 其實點先叫放低  不過的確可以令自己無咁上心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n想知有無巴絲都會咁 明知對方對自己係朋友都表白  <span style=\"font-size: medium;\"> 不過佢的確有講過少少令人誤會嘅野 好似話佢個世界都有我咁 或者佢睇到條片會share比我睇 我問做咩 佢答我因為睇呢條片嗰陣諗起你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實自問對感情呢啲野唔叫敏感 啱識佢嗰陣我有男神 但其實未到中意嗰位男神 佢知道之後 知我為啲野煩會叫我放手 講左一輪 佢話叫我唔好成日做人咁易心軟 即我堅強啲 所以宜家我好堅強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有時會覺得你對我有少少唔同 我講唔到 到宜家都係 其實有時我地都會傾下計 然後大家做左大家sc 第一位 </span> 咁你地會唔會後悔表白？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36d3f8978f121efe6f4ae21d8d7b4acfda370e94","tid":383741,"uid":141235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:05:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e079fefa724556c50d0b03189ce5f89f678392e","tid":383741,"uid":13374,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:12:03.000Z","msg":"表白都係比個期限自己死心姐"},{"pid":"779c9a59318bdb4345773e4117d556f426677d92","tid":383741,"uid":33952,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:14:57.000Z","msg":"冇朋友做了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fc10211d82c10e05fce83749babee43707221d2","tid":383741,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T17:15:59.000Z","msg":"寧願沒擁抱"},{"pid":"95c99be11b38ad1ab0cf1f372399622d1c10d2fc","tid":383741,"uid":141235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":