 />\n點flirt你？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50084770527638a2fc1e2118816cc53c23ab625f","tid":383741,"uid":135780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T20:27:27.000Z","msg":"都係想早死早超生姐"},{"pid":"fd06a476bc9355b32cc713d8a6ef58e092b23d47","tid":383741,"uid":137407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-01T20:29:07.000Z","msg":"最慘係可能我成日話鐘意佢<br />\n佢以為我講笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就算我話宜家我係表白<br />\n佢都話我日日都表白架啦<br />\n有邊日唔表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都唔知宜家咩關係"}]}